title: Narrative

* This example shows a selective expandable TOC with ''custom icons''

* The default chevron icons are overridden using the `$let` widget

* `toc-open-icon` is set to `$:/core/images/fold-button`

* `toc-closed-icon` is set to `$:/core/images/folder`

{{example-overview}}
+
title: Description

Simple TOC Selective Expandable with Custom Icons
+
title: Output

<$let toc-open-icon="$:/core/images/fold-button" toc-closed-icon="$:/core/images/folder">
<div class="tc-table-of-contents">
<<toc-selective-expandable tag:"Contents">>
</div>
</$let>